                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18371023-2405-offence-1 t18371023-cd-198"></join>17th of October</rs>, 1/2 a peck of wheat, value 1<hi rend="italic">s</hi>., the goods of <persName id="t18371023-name-1344" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18371023-name-1344" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
